#Debugging Steps for Visual Studio Code

1. Set up dev environment to work with a valid shopify app.
    a. Set the key and secret to the app
    b. ensure the app url is your current running version of ngrok
2. Run npm run build
3. Navigate to your server.js file
4. In the tool bar at the top select Run->Start Debugging
5. In the dropdown select Node.js

#ctx.session = needs to have the api key and secret included in the createShopifyAuth function